OL,3,CBoat destroyed after 'sectarian' flag
OL,4,Crow
OL,6,FPolice have made three arrests
OL,7,Ffollowing a report of an assault
OL,8,Foutside a boat club in Portballintrae.
OL,10,FThe PSNI said an altercation was
OL,11,Freported at 7.45pm on Monday, 3 of
OL,12,FJune, between a number of men
OL,13,Fconcerning a flag that was displayed
OL,14,Fon a boat in the Beach Road area.
OL,16,FThe boat was then set alight and
OL,17,Fextensively damaged. It is understood
OL,18,Fthe argument was over an Irish
OL,19,Ftricolour.
