OL,4,Crow
OL,6,FPolice are treating it as a "sectarian-
OL,7,Fmotivated hate crime".
OL,9,FOfficers attended the scene on the
OL,10,Fpier and one man was taken to hospital
OL,11,Ffor his injuries.JInspector Armour
OL,12,Fsaid: "Three men aged 25, 63 and 30,
OL,13,Fwere all arrested on suspicion of a
OL,14,Fnumber of offences including criminal
OL,15,Fdamage and assault occasioning actual
OL,16,Fbodily harm.J"The 63-year-old man has
OL,17,Fsince been released on bail, whilst
OL,18,Fthe other two men remain in custody at
OL,19,Fthis time as enquiries continue.
